data.description: Don't miss this gorgeous single family home in desired 55+ Paradise Gardens IV, in the beautiful city of Margate. This gem feature 2 bright and spacious bedrooms, 2 full baths both with shower and one of them handicap equipped, large living and dinning room, a very nice tiled kitchen with newer top of the line appliances, an amazing  Florida room overlooking to a green belt for your relax or to entertain family and friends, large washer and dryer, a brand new A/C and ducts of the entire property has been just installed, all impact windows and sliding doors, all main areas and rooms have laminated floors, freshly painted, one car garage, clubhouse with pool, gym and lots of amenities, very low HOA, quiet and peaceful neighborhood, close to everything. Hurry up, at this price won't last!
